data.description: This spacious, recently updated 3 bedroom, two bath, and two car garage beauty with master on main and bonus room downstairs will not last long.  Get ready for some serious sightseeing and experience the rich history of Silver Comet Trail being only steps away from your cozy fireplace warmed living room in the fall and winter months, and very spacious backyard with large deck and covered metal pergola in the spring and summer months.  Silver Comet Trail runs from Smyrna for 61.5 miles through Cobb, Paulding and Polk counties. The original brick tunnel still exists.    This highly sought after community is nicely tucked away from the hustle and bustle of local shops, but is centrally located where access to popular shopping and dining is only a minutes' drive away.  The open and spacious kitchen has new stainless-steel appliances, ceramic tiling, and new cabinetry. There is a rear bay window that sits off the kitchen and overlooks the spacious backyard. On the opposite end of the kitchen sits the front facing bay windows of the dining room where you can enjoy a morning breakfast, cup of tea or coffee before beginning your day.  This home has many features you must see for yourself or bring your family to imagine their new home. Whatever you decide, do not wait too long because this home is sure to go fast.
